  <description type="morphology">Shrubs, (2.5–)3–5 × 3–7 dm. Stems: caudex absent; aerial flowering stems 0.3–0.7 dm, floccose or glabrous. Leaves: blade oblanceolate to elliptic, (0.8–)1–2(–2.7) × (0.3–)0.4–0.9(–1.2) cm, densely white-tomentose abaxially, floccose or glabrous adaxially, margins not revolute. Inflorescences 3–10 cm; branches floccose or glabrous. Involucres 2.5–3 mm, floccose or glabrous. Flowers 2–2.5 mm; perianth yellow. Achenes 2–2.5 mm.</description>
